creator: Gekkolab
descriptionHtml:
Create and send legally correct invoices in a quick and easy manner. Perfect for any entrepreneur that wants to provide a premium service to his customers and receive payments quicker.

Setup only takes a couple of minutes and afterwards you can:

● Create and send profesional invoices to customers
● Send iDeal payment requests for immediate payment of you invoice
● Keep track of work orders and convert them quickly to invoices
● Send invoices in both PDF and the new UBL format
● Share invoices and payment requests directly via email, whatsapp or any other medium
The Gekko Invoicing app is connected with your personal Gekko account online. Just log in with your email online on getgekko.com and:
● Download overview of your invoices
● Get access to financial reports
● Send professional quotations to your customers to confirm assignments in advance.

Gekko offers you a complete accounting system

The Gekko platform is much more than the Invoicing app alone. The online account and our four mobile apps – Invoicing, Costs, Hours and Trips – enable freelancers and small companies to easily manage their entire accounting process for free: from hours registration to invoicing to mileage tracking. Managing your company with Gekko meets all requirements of the Dutch Belastingdienst.

Gekko cares about your privacy

All your data is safely stored on your smartphone and through a secure connection on our servers in Europe. Always available, always safe.

● Keep track of work orders and convert them quickly to invoices
● Send invoices in both PDF and the new UBL format
● Share invoices and payment requests directly via email, whatsapp or any other medium

Gekko Invoicing is a free application that can be used either as a stand alone invoicing tool or as part of all the other tools in the Gekko family. Gekko offers free tools to freelancers and other small entrepreneurs for:

● KM tracking and other trip tracking via Gekko Trips
● Expense receipt scanning and managing via Gekko Costs
● Time management and hour tracking via Gekko Hours

Gekko provides all these tools to freelancers and other entrepreneurs. Gekko will cover any bookkeeping need you might have. And with your free online account on www.getgekko.com, you will get a full overview of everything you and your company does, from quotations to customer management. A complete bookkeeping system accessible from any device. Accounting without hassle.

All data you add in Gekko Invoicing or anywhere else on Gekko will be stored via a secure connection to European servers. All data will be treated confidentially, will never be shared with any other party without your explicit consent and will remain exclusively your property. Gekko stands for safety and privacy.

Questions, feedback, problems?
We’re here for you: send a message to support@getgekko.com.
